---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Product Grave"
  description="Learn about Product Grave, a pixel-art digital graveyard for dead tech products."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-pixel text-xl md:text-2xl text-grave-bone text-shadow-pixel mb-4">ℹ️ ABOUT</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section class="pixel-card p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-pixel text-sm text-grave-bone mb-4">What is Product Grave?</h2>
        <p class="text-grave-ash leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Product Grave is a digital graveyard for dead tech products. We bury them with honor, analyze their demise, and extract lessons for the living.
        </p>
        <p class="text-grave-ash leading-relaxed">
          Every product on this site has a story — not just data, but a narrative of ambition, mistake, and consequence. We believe failure is the best teacher, but only if you're willing to examine the body.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="pixel-card p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-pixel text-sm text-grave-bone mb-4">Why Pixel Art?</h2>
        <p class="text-grave-ash leading-relaxed">
          Because death deserves style. The pixel aesthetic evokes nostalgia, playfulness, and a certain retro sincerity. These products may be dead, but their stories deserve to be told beautifully.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="pixel-card p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-pixel text-sm text-grave-bone mb-4">Open Source</h2>
        <p class="text-grave-ash leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Product Grave is open source. Our data lives in Markdown files on GitHub. If you spot an error or want to add a product, open a pull request or submit via our form.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/yourorg/productgrave" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="pixel-btn">View on GitHub</a>
      </section>

      <section class="pixel-card p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="font-pixel text-sm text-grave-bone mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-grave-ash leading-relaxed">
          Questions, corrections, or just want to say hi? Reach out on <a href="https://twitter.com/productgrave" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-grave-ghost hover:underline">Twitter/X</a> or via GitHub Issues.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
